									</span>
									<span class="uael-question-f868e34 uael-question-span" tabindex="0" id="uael-faq-1">What is the Total Addressable Market for the Pizza Industry?</span>
								</div>
								<div class="uael-accordion-content" role="tabpanel">
									<span>
									<span><p>The Total Addressable Market for the <a href="https://aaronallen.com/blog/pizza-industry">pizza industry</a> is $160 globally, including only foodservice (excluding pizzas sold in the Food At Home category).</p></span>									</span>
								</div>
							</div>
														<div id="uael-accordion-da40f2e" class="uael-faq-accordion" role="tablist">
								<div class= "uael-accordion-title" aria-expanded="false" role="tab">
									<span class="uael-accordion-icon uael-accordion-icon-left">
										<span class="uael-accordion-icon-closed"><i class="fas fa-angle-right"></i></span>
										<span class="uael-accordion-icon-opened"><i class="fas fa-angle-up"></i></span>
									</span>
									<span class="uael-question-da40f2e uael-question-span" tabindex="0" id="uael-faq-2">What is the TAM for Foodservice Technology?</span>
								</div>
								<div class="uael-accordion-content" role="tabpanel">
									<span>
									<span><p>Currently, the Total Addressable Market for <a href="https://aaronallen.com/restaurant-technology">Foodservice Technology</a> is estimated at $500 billion globally. However, this is a very dynamic industry with new use cases being developed almost daily, and a TAM that expands quickly.</p></span>									</span>
								</div>
							</div>
														<div id="uael-accordion-3993243" class="uael-faq-accordion" role="tablist">
								<div class= "uael-accordion-title" aria-expanded="false" role="tab">
									<span class="uael-accordion-icon uael-accordion-icon-left">
										<span class="uael-accordion-icon-closed"><i class="fas fa-angle-right"></i></span>
										<span class="uael-accordion-icon-opened"><i class="fas fa-angle-up"></i></span>
									</span>
									<span class="uael-question-3993243 uael-question-span" tabindex="0" id="uael-faq-3">What is the TAM for Restaurant Robotics?</span>
								</div>
								<div class="uael-accordion-content" role="tabpanel">
									<span>
									<span><p>In a first stage, the total addressable market for <a href="https://aaronallen.com/blog/restaurant-robotics">restaurant robotics</a> would be close to 287,000 Limited-Service locations in the U.S (with 61,000 units at  large QSR chains).</p></span>									</span>
								</div>
							</div>
