									</span>
									<span class="uael-question-351557e uael-question-span" tabindex="0" id="uael-faq-4">What is the Total Addressable Market for QSR in Europe?</span>
								</div>
								<div class="uael-accordion-content" role="tabpanel">
									<span>
									<span><p>The Fast Food TAM for the UK, Germany, France, Spain, Italy, the Netherlands, Belgium, and Portugal is close to $80 billion.</p></span>									</span>
								</div>
							</div>
